node.text: I get so many questions not only how I style my hair but how I keep it shiny and healthy! As you know, I always use @foxybaehair to style my hair but before adding heat I use their NEW shampoos/conditioners + Cool AF Heat Protectant to keep it healthy, silky and voluminous! If you wanna pick up any of the products from the video use my code YOATZI to save 60% off site wide.
